Name: paranasal sinus disease
Definition: An autosomal dominant disease that is characterized by the growth of numerous noncancerous tumors in many parts of the body.

Name: nasal cavity disease
Definition: An ovarian cancer that originates in the germ (egg) cells of the ovary.

Name: lethal midline granuloma
Definition: A parasitic protozoa infectious disease that involves infection caused by protozoan parasite of the genus Leishmania
